# Verification

## Check A — technical
Run what applies: lint, typecheck (`test:ai` / `typecheck:ai`), unit tests, build, `npm run ai:health`.

## Check B — logical
Re-read the request: requirements met? regressions? architecture fit? excess complexity? docs/memory updated? code/tests/docs aligned?

## Critical changes
Also run an adversarial review pass (what breaks it? edge cases? partial failure? replay?).

Report which checks ran and which did not.
